title: Unidentified Man Robs Baltimore Family Dollar at Gunpoint
text:
Unidentified Man Robs Baltimore Family Dollar at Gunpoint March 4, 2017 1:58 PM Filed Under: Baltimore City Crime , Belair Road , Family Dollar 
BALTIMORE (WJZ)â€“ City police need your help identifying a robbery suspect. 
This robbery occurred on January 29 at 7:50 p.m. at the Dollar General located in the 4800 block of Belair Road. 
The suspect used a revolver to rob the store. No one was injured but the suspect got away with money. 
Anyone who knows the man should call detectives at 410-366-6341 or call Metro Crime Stoppers at 1-866-7LOCKUP.
